short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to collect and display URLs of all open tabs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tab URL Collector is a simple yet powerful Chrome extension designed to make your browsing experience more organized and efficient. With just a click, it collects and displays the URLs of all open tabs in your current Chrome window. You can easily copy these URLs to your clipboard and save or share them as needed.

Features:

1. Collect URLs: Fetches the links of all open tabs in your Chrome browser window.
2. Copy to Clipboard: Quickly copy all the collected URLs with a single button click.
3. Clean and User-Friendly Interface: Designed for simplicity and ease of use.

This tool is perfect for researchers, developers, or anyone managing multiple tabs and looking for a quick way to save or share their browsing sessions.

Install Tab URL Collector and simplify your browsing workflow today!
